resources.string:
PK L H XXX000

PK – parking payments in Kaunas city;

L – parking duration in hours and minutes:
0.15 – 15 min; 0.3 – 30 min;
0.45 – 45 min; 1 – 1 h;
1.15 – 1 h 15 min etc.

H – parking zone:

G – yellow zone.
A – orange zone,
R – red zone,
M – blue zone,
Z – green zone;

XXX000 – license plate number (it is written without spaces).
